    "authored_hints": "[{\"hint_class\":null,\"hint_markdown\":\"The <code style=\\\"color:black; background-color:#EBD546\\\">location</code> block is attached to the <code style=\\\"color:black; background-color:#F79EA5\\\">make new sprite</code> block.\\n\\nTo change a sprite's location, click the pin on the location block, then click where you want it to go.\\n\\n![](https://images.code.org/e3267d2b50f754befc63744be14287ac-image-1633360873408.gif)\",\"hint_id\":\"hint1\",\"hint_type\":\"general\",\"hint_path\":\"\",\"hint_video\":\"\",\"tts_url\":\"https://tts.code.org/sharon22k/180/100/6a3d28d49993d626efaf4da56640ea75/csc_bookcover_say_2023.mp3\"}]",
    "long_instructions": "**Add a sprite to bring the main character of this book onto the cover!** \r\n- Connect a <code style=\"color:black; background-color:#F79EA5\">make new sprite</code> block under the <code style=\"color:black; background-color:#B3B2FB\">set background</code> block. \r\n\r\n- Click the pin on the attached <code style=\"color:black; background-color:#EBD546\">location</code> block. \r\n- Then click where you want the sprite to go. <img src=\"https://images.code.org/51ad72f6ba72c16b8094566622e310ab-image-1683905416875.gif\" style=\"width: 20%; float: right; padding-top: 20px\">\r\n- Press <code style=\"color:black; background-color:#FFBD46\">Run</code>.  \r\n\r\n",
